    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very strong; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major systems are fully functional. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of use consistent with its age, such as minor paint chips and slight wear on the upholstery, it remains a clean and reliable car. This is a great option for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that is ready to be driven immediately without any urgent repairs needed.",
