    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner ready for a significant project. The engine currently struggles to stay running and exhibits several active fluid leaks, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Cosmetically, the body has visible rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, recommended for parts or a complete overhaul.",
      "price": 4800.0,
